{"type": "article", "id": 26307, "title": "四季餐桌", "description": "餐桌布置一直都是社交中的重头戏。餐具与器皿的放置、鲜花与饰品的搭配，能提升生活的幸福感。在这个颜值先行的时代，餐桌也要有型有款。", "date": "2016-05-07T08:25:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27075, "name": "餐桌布置"}, {"id": 27076, "name": "餐桌设计"}, {"id": 197, "name": "餐饮"}], "category": 17, "column": 29, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 124, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121933lISoLPEnVzX3g2uB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2><b>作者简介</b></h2>\n<p>凯瑟琳娜·林德伯格·本汉德森，瑞典餐桌艺术家、作家。曾是著名服装设计师，设计的儿童连体衣为瑞典皇室专用。还在 2012 年获得了厨艺奥林匹克大赛的金牌。目前专攻餐桌造型，为米其林餐厅、高级酒店和大型宴会做餐桌设计和花艺设计，还参加电视台的 TV 秀，进行著作出版等工作 。</p>\n<p>2012 年获得爱尔福特奥林匹克最佳桌面布置金勋章。</p>\n<p>前后出版了 6 本著作，为 NOMA 在内的高级餐厅和酒店进行餐桌艺术的授课和培训。在瑞典电视台有很多 TV SHOW 节目。</p>\n<h2>内文插图</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121927wLt27JMrykPUD0mX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121928WH273jfPE49KsL5q.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121928CLFVvWDGR46adfn3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031219296sngrHD41lwxiECj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.659\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121929juvFw4s7y6KYnxB5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121930naBUYj4EwhGgNJOT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121930OyYKSMZcf89NqQ1I.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121931a0zGYuDOJ2XrH7Cn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121931w0L3pKMXmRqIZ5ot.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121932QhSeys6rLWJPFnMq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121932Nh73ZuTFaxjprBft.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n"}